ource=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国官僚转向人工智能、手写机器人来处理官方文书工作</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3253662/chinas-bureaucrats-turn-ai-handwriting-robots-cope-official-paperwork?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>虽然这些工具对于一些平凡的任务很有用，但它们由于没有接受最新信息的培训而受到限制。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 04:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3253662/chinas-bureaucrats-turn-ai-handwriting-robots-cope-official-paperwork?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国房地产：房主转向社交媒体以提高在低迷市场中快速出售的机会</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/business/china-business/article/3253776/china-property-homeowners-turn-social-media-boost-their-chances-quick-sale-depressed-market?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在二手房市场低迷、供大于求、价格跌至新低的情况下，中国许多房主开始通过社交媒体出售房产，希望更快地找到买家并达成更好的交易。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 03:30:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/business/china-business/article/3253776/china-property-homeowners-turn-social-media-boost-their-chances-quick-sale-depressed-market?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国将军对中国太空技术的“惊人”增长发出警告</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3253945/us-general-raises-alarm-over-breathtaking-growth-chinas-space-tech?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>美国太空司令部司令史蒂芬·怀廷表示，到 2030 年，中国将在大多数太空技术领域达到世界一流水平。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 02:00:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3253945/us-general-raises-alarm-over-breathtaking-growth-chinas-space-tech?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国的C919喷气式飞机如何体现出规避美国限制并超越全球领先者的雄心</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3253867/how-chinas-c919-jet-reflects-ambitions-skirt-us-restrictions-and-soar-beyond-global-leaders?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>随着波音-空客双头垄断，这家中国本土窄体飞机制造商正在东南亚宣传其进步，但必须克服哪些挑战？</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 00:00:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3253867/how-chinas-c919-jet-reflects-ambitions-skirt-us-restrictions-and-soar-beyond-global-leaders?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>致命的渔船失事并不是习近平在台海遭遇的第一起悲剧，但紧张局势使两国关系更难修复</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3253946/fatal-fishing-boat-crash-isnt-first-tragedy-test-xi-jinping-taiwan-strait-tensions-make-ties-harder?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>台湾海岸警卫队与中国大陆渔民之间的冲突与习近平在1990年处理的紧急情况有一些相似之处，但分析人士表示，北京和台北之间缺乏信任可能会使这次的解决更加困难。</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 22:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3253946/fatal-fishing-boat-crash-isnt-first-tragedy-test-xi-jinping-taiwan-strait-tensions-make-ties-harder?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>白宫竞选考验中美关系，但北京不会利用“两会”发表对选举的看法</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3253947/white-house-race-tests-us-china-ties-beijing-wont-use-two-sessions-air-opinions-election?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>年度政治会议是北京宣示外交政策立场的平台，但分析人士预计，拜登对美国总统竞选持中立立场，因为拜登与特朗普的复赛不会给双边关系带来多少缓解。</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 14:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3253947/white-house-race-tests-us-china-ties-beijing-wont-use-two-sessions-air-opinions-election?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国免去香港事务资深人士张晓明的最高咨询机构高级职务</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3253954/china-removes-hong-kong-affairs-veteran-zhang-xiaoming-senior-role-top-advisory-body?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>张仍然是共产党员和政协委员，但不再担任该机构的副秘书长。</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 13:27:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3253954/china-removes-hong-kong-affairs-veteran-zhang-xiaoming-senior-role-top-advisory-body?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>“两会”倒计时，中国官方媒体积极推动经济发展</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3253941/chinas-state-media-positive-economic-spin-mode-countdown-two-sessions?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>共产党喉舌称负面因素增多，但国家正处于良好复苏之中。</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 13:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3253941/chinas-state-media-positive-economic-spin-mode-countdown-two-sessions?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国航天员在天宫空间站徒步修复受损太阳能电池板</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3253937/chinese-astronauts-take-walk-fix-damaged-solar-panel-tiangong-space-station?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>神舟十七号机组的两名成员离开空间站八个小时，以完成去年 12 月开始的维修工作。</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 13:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3253937/chinese-astronauts-take-walk-fix-damaged-solar-panel-tiangong-space-station?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国科学家研制出强大的耐寒锂电池</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3253745/chinese-scientists-produce-powerful-winter-proof-lithium-battery?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>研究人员开发出了一种电解质，可以帮助电动汽车电池在极端条件下运行。</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 10:00:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3253745/chinese-scientists-produce-powerful-winter-proof-lithium-battery?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国科学家揭开华为可折叠智能手机“液体装甲”秘密</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3253606/chinese-scientists-reveal-liquid-armour-secret-huaweis-foldable-smartphone?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>研究人员开发了一种尖端材料内层，该内层在受到冲击时会立即硬化，然后再恢复到柔性状态。</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 08:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3253606/chinese-scientists-reveal-liquid-armour-secret-huaweis-foldable-smartphone?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>由于士气低落，中国习近平呼吁年轻官员“忠诚和诚实”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3253931/chinas-xi-jinping-calls-loyalty-and-honesty-younger-officials-morale-runs-low?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>他还鼓励中青年干部创新，远离腐败，因为共产党官员面临着反腐运动和经济放缓带来的越来越大的压力。</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 06:37:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3253931/chinas-xi-jinping-calls-loyalty-and-honesty-younger-officials-morale-runs-low?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item></channel></rss>